  "prompt": "Who is best in Sachin, virat and dhoni?",
  "response": "Determining who is \"best\" among Sachin Tendulkar, Virat Kohli, and Mahendra Singh Dhoni is subjective and depends on various factors, including personal preference, statistical achievements, and impact on the game.\n\n1. **Sachin Tendulkar**: Widely regarded as one of the greatest batsmen in cricket history, he holds numerous records, including being the highest run-scorer in international cricket. His career spanned 24 years, and he is known for his technical proficiency and incredible consistency.\n\n2. **Virat Kohli**: Renowned for his aggressive batting style and chasing ability, Kohli has broken several records, especially in limited-overs formats. He is known for his fitness and intense competitiveness and has received accolades for his leadership as well.\n\n3. **Mahendra Singh Dhoni**: As a captain, Dhoni is celebrated for his calm demeanor and strategic acumen, leading India to victories in the 2007 ICC World T20 and the 2011 ICC Cricket World Cup. He is also recognized for his finishing skills in matches and his wicketkeeping abilities.\n\nEach player's greatness can be viewed through different lenses: Tendulkar for his records and longevity, Kohli for his modern batting prowess and competitive spirit, and Dhoni for his leadership and finishing abilities. Ultimately, the \"best\" player might vary based on personal opinions and the aspects of cricket one values most.",
